Wag the Dog;;76;;86;;R;;Two weeks prior to reelection, the United States president lands in the middle of a sex scandal. In need of outside help to quell the situation, presidential adviser Winifred Ames (Anne Heche) enlists the expertise of spin doctor Conrad Brean (Robert De Niro), who decides a distraction is the best course of action. Brean approaches Hollywood producer Stanley Motss (Dustin Hoffman) to help him fabricate a war in Albania -- and once underway, the duo has the media entirely focused on the war.;;Drama,Comedy;;Barry Levinson;;1997;;Dustin Hoffman,Robert De Niro,Anne Heche,Woody Harrelson,Denis Leary,Willie Nelson,Andrea Martin,Michael Belson,Suzanne Cryer,John Michael Higgins,Suzie Plakson,Kirsten Dunst,William H. Macy;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/wag_the_dog